title: The Kardashians: Billion Dollar Industry
overview: Arguably the most influential family of the 21st Century and certainly one of the most profitable, how have The Kardashians defied their critics to build a family brand and earned their fortune?This two-part documentary features rarely-seen archive and candid insight from close friends and former colleagues, revealing the deals and decisions that increased the family's finances as they grew from reality stars to billionaire business owners.Â
